<p>Hi Emil,</p>
<p>Here's the cool thing about using a tool made by a small team:</p>
<p>Your feedback and requests actually influence the product. Every one of these updates were based on conversations we've been having with you ♡</p>
<p><strong>Right click to copy images</strong></p>
<img src="https://carbon-media.accelerator.net/00000000001/0IdgvvScnNFcb1bR0ueAfN;1000x_.jpeg?auto=webp" width="960" height="463" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;"/>
<p>✦ You can now right click an image card directly from the main grid and copy it to your clipboard on desktop. Please don't ask us why we didn't ship this sooner.</p>
<p><strong>Top of mind on mobile</strong></p>
<img src="https://carbon-media.accelerator.net/00000000001/6kmVsvQwAIIfk8lih7K0Ok;870x540.jpeg?auto=webp" width="960" height="463" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;"/>
<p>✦ We received dozens of emails from you about missing TOM on your mobile screens. <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nBdeR3omNTE">Now he's back! </a> On both iPhone and Android.</p>
<p>✦ Use Top of Mind to prioritize your todo list, an article you want to come back to, a quote inspiring you this week.</p>
<p><strong>Personalize your note typeface</strong></p>
<img src="https://carbon-media.accelerator.net/00000000001/11NhZ0CS8vPez3Nonm5A0B;870x540.jpeg?auto=webp" width="960" height="463" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;"/>
<p>You can now personalize the typeface for your note cards to make it more YOU. You'll find four different options under Settings on desktop. Which one are you choosing?</p>
<p><strong>Support for arXiv links</strong></p>
<img src="https://carbon-media.accelerator.net/00000000001/gI9ZITjFvWOeFDH26nnY8N;870x540.jpeg?auto=web" width="960" height="463" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;"/>
<p>✦  A highly requested one for our researchers. Save arXiv links with a click and you'll have the full PDF paper in your mind, meaning:</p>
<p>✔ Your own private PDF copy<br />
✔ Analyzed with TLDR summary<br />
✔ Automatic AI tags<br />
✔ Indexed for easy search recall</p>
<p><strong>Automatic quote recognition</strong></p>
<img src="https://carbon-media.accelerator.net/00000000001/gX3cRVG4uhgf464zdgzBCO;870x540.jpeg?auto=webp" width="960" height="463" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;"/>
<p>✦  Save a QUOTE without an attribution, and now your mind automatically tries to find and add the author. (Currently in beta - it will get better!)</p>
<p>✦ Quotes are also analyzed + enriched now with additional context and automatic tags for better recall.</p>
<p>We hope you're as excited about all these little updates as we are. Lots more to come in the new year, which we'll talk about in our next email (:</p>
